Articles of Confederation
with a federal constitution

00:00:09.254 --> 00:00:12.618
were met with fierce opposition.

00:00:13.073 --> 00:00:15.096
So, what's off here is what was met

00:00:15.096 --> 00:00:16.973
with fierce opposition?

00:00:16.973 --> 00:00:19.620
Well, the proposal,
the proposal to replace

00:00:19.620 --> 00:00:21.153
the existing Articles of Confederation

00:00:21.153 --> 00:00:22.557
with a federal constitution.

00:00:22.557 --> 00:00:24.310
The proposal is what is being met

00:00:24.310 --> 00:00:26.829
with fierce opposition.

00:00:26.829 --> 00:00:29.330
Now the proposal, this is clearly,

00:00:29.330 --> 00:00:32.174
we're talking about one
proposal, the proposal.

00:00:32.174 --> 00:00:35.745
This is right over here
is singular, singular.

00:00:35.745 --> 00:00:37.962
While this right over,
they're saying were met.

00:00:37.962 --> 00:00:40.133
Well, one thing, you wouldn't use were,

00:00:40.133 --> 00:00:42.908
