00:00:42.908 --> 00:00:47.134
that's it's happening to,
that it's being met with.

00:00:47.134 --> 00:00:48.898
So this right over here,

00:00:48.898 --> 00:00:52.779
this verb is for plural.

00:00:52.779 --> 00:00:54.765
This is for if we had many proposals.

00:00:54.765 --> 00:00:56.990
If this said, the proposals
to replace the existing

00:00:56.990 --> 00:01:00.658
Articles of Confederation were
met with fierce opposition,

00:01:00.658 --> 00:01:01.900
then that would make sense.

00:01:01.900 --> 00:01:03.862
But this needs to be singular.

00:01:03.862 --> 00:01:05.047
So let's look at the options.

00:01:05.047 --> 00:01:06.640
So we definitely don't like it as is,

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:08.041
