00:01:10.212 --> 00:01:13.082
that is where the verb

00:01:13.082 --> 00:01:17.723
matches the singular noun.

00:01:17.723 --> 00:01:21.864
So let's see, at the
Constitutional Convention of 1787,

00:01:21.864 --> 00:01:23.954
the proposal, and you know, we could even

00:01:23.954 --> 00:01:25.869
for the sake of kind
of thinking about this,

